{"tid":234630,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"求救!台灣入台證一問","createTime":"2017-05-08T12:20:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T09:02:35.000Z","uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b092e8e3951f8b4371b81335770e14e052bf3fb","tid":234630,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T12:20:18.000Z","msg":"小弟曾經申請過台灣居留證（讀書），之後係未領取張證之前已經放棄無讀（得張紙）<br />\n咁居留期授權到2018年<br />\n<br />\n咁最近買左機票想去台灣玩，但網上申請入台證時話我有居留權，唔比整入台證<br />\n<br />\n咁我打過去金鐘果邊 佢話要先寄信去台灣取消居留證先可以用觀光身份申請入台證去台灣<br />\n現有居留證因為唔係讀書唔用得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我打算聽朝一早就去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴絲試過 一般要搞幾耐？<br />\n機票買左18號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f004ccf5843a2d0523cc059dedaa6d0162debf47","tid":234630,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T12:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016e6f5e2e6d522f8dac89eaab8d5ab3436403c2","